hw2: Procedural Textures

based on:
ex03: Procedural Textures

Kyle Curtis
CSCI4239/5239 Spring 2026

Demonstrates the use of shaders to generate textures


Key bindings
  m          Toggle shaders
  o          Change objects
  p			 Change Perspective/Orthogonal
  s			 Stop light's movement
  h			 Changes Hologram Spec
  xXyYzZ     Change location or zoom
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit

  time spent: 6 hour